  "description": "Check for file formatting errors and to submit annual returns for employment related securities (ERS) schemes and arrangements.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>Employers, or agents acting on their behalf, can use this service to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>check files for formatting errors at any time</li>\n  <li>submit annual employment related securities (<abbr title=\"Employment related securities\">ERS</abbr>) returns after the end of the tax year</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The tax year runs from 6 April to 5 April the next year. You then have until midnight on 6 July to submit your annual return. If you do not, you or your employees may lose any tax advantages from the scheme.</p>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p>To use this service you need a Government Gateway user ID and password. If you do not have a user ID, you can create one at the start of the service.</p>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://www.tax.service.gov.uk/gg/sign-in?continue=/business-account/&origin=ERS-frontend",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "will_continue_on": "the HMRC service"
  },
